    "body": "> I'm nervous about the lack of tests on the `runner` package. What do you think about moving those over from `provisionerd_test.go`?\r\n\r\n@kylecarbs From what I looked, there's relatively high coverage via existing `provisionerd` tests, but I agree it might be good to test out some of the functionality. For example, `ForceStop()` seems to be lacking coverage: https://codecov.io/gh/coder/coder/compare/d9668f7a4ef81ea22fcf27fd188a25e8eae45327...164a3024fe52aa47af23a9605d8b2238a2ad78a6/diff",
