  {
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Seems _fine_ to me. I use VS Code's test gutters to check what is/isn't covered, and it works pretty well, so I'm sad this won't appear there.\r\n\r\nI think we make an issue for it, then this looks good to me!",
